OL,3,CBank keeps interest rates at 5.25% and
OL,4,Cwants 'more evidence' before further
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe Bank of England has decided to
OL,8,Fhold UK interest rates at 5.25%, but
OL,9,Fgave a sense of optimism that
OL,10,Fborrowing costs could soon be cut, ITV
OL,11,FNews Economics Editor Joel Hills has
OL,12,Fmore
OL,14,FIt's a hold. But one that leaves the
OL,15,Fdoor open for an interest rate cut in
OL,16,FJune.
