OL,3,CBank keeps interest rates at 5.25% and
OL,4,Cwants 'more evidence' before further
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe headline rate of inflation fell to
OL,8,F3.2% in March and the Bank of England
OL,9,Fthinks it is set to fall further,
OL,10,Freaching touching distance of its 2%
OL,11,Ftarget "within the next couple of
OL,12,Fmonths".
OL,14,FSeven members of the Monetary Policy
OL,15,FCommittee (MPC) voted to keep the rate
OL,16,Fat 5.25%. Two of them voted for a cut.
OL,18,FThe balance of opinions has shifted
OL,19,Fslightly since March with Dave Ramsden
OL,20,Fjoining Swati Dhingra in feeling it's
OL,21,Ftime to ease off.
