OL,7,FFood and fuel inflation - both
OL,8,Fsignificant drivers of soaring overall
OL,9,Finflation in the UK - are now coming
OL,10,Fdown again.
OL,12,FThe fall in the OFGEM price cap in
OL,13,FApril is bringing bills down but the
OL,14,FBank assumes the cap is unlikely to
OL,15,Ffall further.
