OL,7,FConsumer prices are beginning to
OL,8,Fstabilise, albeit at a much higher
OL,9,Flevel than three years ago, and the
OL,10,Foutlook for economic growth 90.5% this
OL,11,Fyear and 1% in 2025) looks weak but
OL,12,Fthe MPC wants to see more compelling
OL,13,Fproof that inflation has been tamed
OL,14,Fbefore it cuts.
OL,16,FThe Bank believes the inflationary
OL,17,Ffull impact of the both the pandemic
OL,18,Fand Russia's invasion of Ukraine has
OL,19,Fnow been felt.
