OL,7,FWhat remains is a lingering concern
OL,8,Fthat inflation is feeding itself
OL,9,Fdomestically.
OL,11,FThe Bank worries about the tightness
OL,12,Fof the Labour Market, although it
OL,13,Fconcede that the ratio of vacancies to
OL,14,Fjobseekers in the UK has fallen back
OL,15,Fto pre-Covid levels.
OL,17,FIt also worries about annual pay
OL,18,Fgrowth and inflation in the Services
OL,19,Fsector of the economy, both of which
OL,20,Fare running above 6% a year.
