OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,F"We need to see more evidence that
OL,8,Finflation will stay low before we can
OL,9,Fcut interest rates," explains the
OL,10,FGovernor, Andrew Bailey. "I'm
OL,11,Foptimistic that things are moving in
OL,12,Fthe right direction".
OL,14,FAnyone with a mortgage will be wishing
OL,15,Fthings would move a little more
OL,16,Fquickly.
OL,18,FThe next interest rate decision will
OL,19,Fbe announced on June 20.
