OL,7,FAnyone hoping for a nod that interest
OL,8,Frates cuts are imminent or clues as to
OL,9,Fhow quickly rates are likely to fall
OL,10,Fand where they might settle is likely
OL,11,Fto be disappointed by what the Bank
OL,12,Fhas to say.
OL,14,FThe MPC is keeping its options open
OL,15,Fand promising only to follow the data.
