OL,7,FBank Rate remains at 5.25%. Andrew
OL,8,FBailey has said previously that one
OL,9,Fcut would leave rates in "restrictive"
OL,10,Fterritory? What about two or three? At
OL,11,Fwhat level do interest rate cease to
OL,12,Fbe restrictive? The Bank won't say.
OL,14,FOn the face of it, there's plenty of
OL,15,Froom for the bank to ease off the
OL,16,Faccelerator but we still don't know
OL,17,Fwhat "neutral" looks like.
